				<h2 class="title icon">
					<img src="http://forum.opiophile.org/images/icons/icon6.gif" alt="Default" /> Re: First time with methadone--how much to take?
				</h2>
				


						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_38536">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							Depends on your personal tolerance level...but just as a comparison, when I was in the 100mg of OC range, a 40mg methadone wafer would be enough to fucker me up good. It is some pretty strong stuff, and it takes a lot longer to come on, so be ready for that. Also, methadone has a very long half-life in your body, so be careful if you're gonna do multiple days/doses. But you will enjoy the high if that's what you're after.<br />
<br />
<br />
ZK
						</blockquote>
