						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							Yea,30~40mg would probabley be a safe singular dose,for a day.And should'nt fuck you up for work the next day.But take Zodiackiller advice air on the side of caution,Methadone is a real creeper,don't start re-dosing yourself if the effects don't hit you as quick as you'd like.And injesting Methadone for the first time be extra carefull with this drug, make sure you've got people around you.(just in case)Better safe than sorry.<br />
And remember Methadone has a half life that can last over 36hrs so if you felt that your first dose did sweet Fuck all.Don't go Berzerk the following day.Stay safe.<br />
