						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							<b>Note - this is an old thread</b><br />
 <br />
I saw someone reading this, checked and couldn't find a quick answer so:<br />
 <br />
First time opiate niaive thrillseekers should take an oral dose from <b>15-20 mgs</b>, depending on body weight. <b>Then wait for 3 hours</b>. If you are still not satisfied and you don't feel nauseous when you drink a glass of water, have another 5 mgs and <b>stop</b> there!<br />
 <br />
That's it. Be safe and <b>DON'T keep dosing</b>. <b>Don't have any benzos. Don't have any alcohol.</b> <br />
 <br />
If you feel good then <b>don't attempt this the next day as it will accumulate! - </b>Wait at least 14 days before trying again if you wish to feel the same thing and repeat it.<br />
 <br />
<font color="red"><b>You have been warned. <u>If you mess up then you will feel sick for 36 hours or you might OD/<font size="4">die</font>.</u> </b></font><font color="black">So take it easy!!!!</font>
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
